{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Event.preventDefault()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\"><code>Event()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/bubbles\"><code>bubbles</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelable\"><code>cancelable</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelBubble\"><code>cancelBubble</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>composed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/currentTarget\"><code>currentTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/defaultPrevented\"><code>defaultPrevented</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/eventPhase\"><code>eventPhase</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/explicitOriginalTarget\"><code>explicitOriginalTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/isTrusted\"><code>isTrusted</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/originalTarget\"><code>originalTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/returnValue\"><code>returnValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/srcElement\"><code>srcElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/target\"><code>target</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>composedPath()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/initEvent\"><code>initEvent()</code></a></li><li><em><code>preventDefault()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopImmediatePropagation\"><code>stopImmediatePropagation()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopPropagation\"><code>stopPropagation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cancela o evento se for cancelável, sem parar a propagação do mesmo.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>event</em>.preventDefault();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Alternar é a ação padrão de clicar em uma caixa de seleção. Este exemplo demonstra como impedir que isso aconteça:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>preventDefault example<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">stopDefAction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">evt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    evt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-checkbox'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> stopDefAction<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Please click on the checkbox control.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>my-checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>my-checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Checkbox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Você pode ver o&nbsp;<code>preventDefault</code> em ação&nbsp;<a class=\"internal external\" href=\"https://media.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/samples/domref/dispatchEvent.html\" title=\"samples/domref/dispatchEvent.html\" rel=\" noopener\">aqui</a>.</p>\n\n<p>O exemplo a seguir demonstra como um input com texto inválido pode ser parado ao chegar ao campo de entrada com o&nbsp;preventDefault().</p>\n\n<div id=\"preventdefault_invalid_text\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>preventDefault example<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Init</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myTextbox <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-textbox'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    myTextbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'keypress'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> checkName<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">checkName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">evt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> charCode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> evt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>charCode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>charCode <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>charCode <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">97</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> charCode <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">122</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            evt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"Please use lowercase letters only.\"</span>\n                <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"charCode: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> charCode <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onload</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">Init</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Please enter your name using lowercase letters only.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>my-textbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Aqui está o resultado do código anterior:</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"preventDefault invalid text sample\" id=\"frame_preventdefault_invalid_text\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault/_sample_.preventdefault_invalid_text.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Chamar preventDefault durante qualquer fase do fluxo de eventos cancela o evento, o que significa que qualquer ação padrão normalmente feita pela aplicação como um resultado do evento não ocorrerá.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>Nota:</strong> A partir do <span title=\"(Firefox 6.0 / Thunderbird 6.0 / SeaMonkey 2.3)\">Gecko&nbsp;6.0</span>, chamar o&nbsp;<code>preventDefault()</code>&nbsp;faz com que o&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/defaultPrevented\"><code>event.defaultPrevented</code></a> se torne true.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Você pode usar o&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelable\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/event.cancelable\">event.cancelable</a> para checar se o evento é cancelável. Chamar o&nbsp;<code>preventDefault</code>&nbsp;para um evento não cancelável&nbsp;não fará efeito.</p>\n\n<p><code>Se o&nbsp;preventDefault não parar a propagação do evento através do DOM. event.stopPropagation deve ser usada para isso.</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-Event-preventDefault\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Events: preventDefault</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notes"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Cancela o evento se for cancelável, sem parar a propagação do mesmo.","popularity":0.0025,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"event.preventDefault","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"event.preventDefault","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Event.preventDefault()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/event/preventdefault","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/event/preventdefault/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event","title":"Event"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault","title":"Event.preventDefault()"}],"pageTitle":"Event.preventDefault() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}